702239f-a.text:
Third Ave., east side, from and including State Street, to, but not including Schermerhorn Street. Also shown is State Street, at and adjoining the N.E. corner of Third Ave. This is a view of Public School No. 15. In the right background of State Street, is the Williamsburg Savings Bank Building.
